title: New: RaneRaps – Sunrise (Prod. by Sndwvs)
body:
LA’s **RaneRaps** merges the intensity of Kendrick and the playfulness of Chance on his latest track, _Sunrise_.

With a new EP expected this fall, this newest cut is a big step forward, and takes his sound into pretty exciting territories. Check out Sunrise below.

Like this? Follow our [On Repeat Playlist](https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02) for a handpicked selection of the very best in new music; updated weekly.
